# Gracelyn University — Ambassador Scaling Program
# Copy to a secure location and set these in the Catalyst Console
# (Configurations -> Environment Variables). DO NOT commit a filled-in .env.
# These are SECRETS. Never paste real values into the repo, issues, or PRs.
#
# Canonical names only. Aliases found in the design docs (CLAUDE_API_KEY,
# OPENAI_ASSISTANT_ID, HEYGEN_AVATAR_ID, META_ACCESS_TOKEN) are intentionally
# NOT used. Ad spend is split per-platform (META_/GOOGLE_DAILY_SPEND_THRESHOLD).
#
# severity: critical = blocks Agent 5A go/no-go; warn = surfaced, non-blocking.

